THE FORCE IS WITH POLICE PSYCHOLOGIST 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Your article "A Force of One" (July 18) is outstanding and true. Dr. Larry 
Blum is one police psychologist who definitely is a tremendous help to the thin 
blue line who serve and protect on a daily basis. 
</P>
<P>
 I have known Larry for 16 years and he has helped untold numbers of officers 
and, yes, one police chief -- me -- to return from the brink of disaster 
because of the lifestyle we adopt in this stressful profession. 
</P>
<P>
 Thanks for sharing Larry with your general readership -- he is definitely one 
of our heroes. 
</P>
