the suspect, who brandished an automatic handgun when the door was opened, 
Deputy Jerardo Gomez said. At the gunman's orders, Jolicoeur filled the thief's 
paper bag with money and then got under a desk while the suspect continued 
rifling the office, Gomez said. 
</P>
<P>
