<HEADLINE>
<P>
FOR THE RECORD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Cancer research -- Dr. Hoda Anton-Culver was incorrectly identified Thursday 
in a story about a $1.1-million National Cancer Institute grant to UC Irvine to 
study colorectal cancer. She is a UCI professor of epidemiology. 
